attributes.Description: An open-world action-adventure game set in the Wild West, following the story of outlaw Arthur Morgan and the Van der Linde gang.
A critically acclaimed action role-playing game where you play as Geralt of Rivia, a monster hunter, in a vast fantasy world filled with rich storytelling
Set in feudal Japan, this action-adventure game follows Jin Sakai, a samurai warrior on a quest to protect Tsushima Island during the Mongol invasion.
A post-apocalyptic action-adventure game that follows Joel and Ellie as they navigate a dangerous world infected by a fungal pandemic.
An upcoming action role-playing game created by FromSoftware in collaboration with George R. R. Martin, set in a dark fantasy world.
A futuristic open-world RPG set in the dystopian Night City, where players take on the role of V in a narrative-driven adventure.
A first-person shooter game part of the Call of Duty series, focusing on modern warfare and intense multiplayer action.
:A survival horror game where players explore a derelict plantation inhabited by a disturbed family, mixing exploration and puzzle-solving.
A first-person survival horror game where you navigate through an abandoned psychiatric hospital using only a camera.
A medieval action RPG that combines strategy, battles, and diplomacy in a sandbox world.
An action-adventure game where players assume the role of Batman in a vast, open-world Gotham City filled with iconic villains.
A survival horror game set in the Alien universe, where players must evade a single xenomorph aboard a space station.
A reimagining of the classic survival horror game, following Leon Kennedy as he tries to save the President's daughter from a sinister cult.
A third-person shooter that continues the story of Max Payne, a former NYPD detective battling his inner demons.
An action-adventure game set during the American Revolution, where players embody Connor, a Native American Assassin.
Set in ancient Egypt, this action RPG explores the origins of the Assassin Brotherhood and follows Bayek on his quest for vengeance.
An open-world action-adventure game set in the fictional state of San Andreas, following the lives of three criminals as they commit heists and navigate a vast world.
